  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Callable<RuntimeActionResult>

    public class ReplyFileMessage
extends PostFileMessage
    A RuntimeAction that replies to a message by uploading a file using the input Slack channel.

    This action relies on the provided JarvisSession to retrieve the Slack channel associated to the user input.

    This class relies on the SlackPlatform's Slack client and Slack bot API token to connect to the Slack API and upload the reply file.

    Note: this class requires that its containing SlackPlatform has been loaded with a valid Slack bot API token in order to authenticate the bot an upload messages.

        Constructs a new ReplyFileMessage with the provided runtimePlatform, session, message, and file.
        Parameters:
        runtimePlatform - the SlackPlatform containing this action
        session - the JarvisSession associated to this action
        message - the message to associated to the uploaded File
